@startuml
title Viaverse Auth — Component Diagram

component "KMP / Next.js Client" as Client
component "API Gateway / App BFF" as BFF
component "AuthController" as AuthApi
component "Auth Use Cases" as UseCases
component "Auth / Capability Policies" as Policies
component "Application Ports\nOtpSender / TokenService / AccountRepo" as Ports
database "PostgreSQL\nAccount / Session / Consent" as DB
database "Valkey / Redis\nOTP / rate limit / revocation" as Redis
component "Netgsm / SES / OAuth Providers" as Providers
queue "Outbox + Kafka\nOtpVerified / SessionCreated" as Kafka
component "Admin BFF / Security Admin" as Admin

Client --> BFF : HTTPS
BFF --> AuthApi : REST
AuthApi --> UseCases : command/query
UseCases --> Policies : validate / authorize
Policies --> Ports : use ports
Ports --> DB : JPA adapter
Ports --> Redis : cache / rate limit
Ports --> Providers : provider adapters
UseCases --> Kafka : outbox events
Admin --> AuthApi : admin security actions

note bottom
Boundary rule:
Domain/application logic never imports provider SDKs.
Providers are infrastructure adapters behind ports.
end note
@enduml
